            "title": "貝索斯稱AI投資熱潮是一場泡沫 長遠看將造福社會",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"貝索斯稱AI投資熱潮是一場泡沫 長遠看將造福社會\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n04M5cL_9IyzBO8cCzbvAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/ee5c1f80-a0cd-11f0-9cdd-5c548b9e0d09\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">貝索斯稱AI投資熱潮是一場泡沫 長遠看將造福社會</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
